</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>4. Check operation of each door oscillator in active test.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000XUF008X" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>5. Door oscillator circuit</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000001P8V004X" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="1" morerows="7" colsep="1" valign="middle" align="left">
<ptxt>Key reminder buzzer does not sound.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>1. Perform ACTIVE TEST for the combination meter.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM0000012G700DX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>2. Check "D DOR CTY SW" in the DATA LIST of the power door lock control system.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000TNZ00BX" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>3. Check the key reminder buzzer when the engine switch is on (ACC) and the drivers door is opened.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>4. Check if the steering wheel is locked when all power supplies are OFF and the drivers door is opened.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>5. Refer to PROBLEM SYMPTOMS TABLE of the steering lock system ("Steering wheel cannot be locked").</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000XWP008X" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>6. Check that the "LCK BAR STUCK" item in the DATA LIST of the certification ECU displays OK.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>
<xref href="RM000000XWV008X" label="XX-XX"/>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>7. Replace the steering lock ECU.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep="1">
<entry colname="2" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>8. Replace the certification ECU.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname="3" colsep="1" align="left">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
